title: need one more person for serious ranked 5s gold-silver
body:
we currently need one more person for ranked 5s, better if you can use skype, normally doing ranked 5s around 7-11 during weekend in Perth time. add me if you want to join us, :) 
my name: warring kingdoms

replies.body:
hey, i fill in solo ranked but main mid/adc/jung in that order, im looking for an active 5s team and am based in sydney. i will be on most nights and use skype and T.S if need b. I am currently s4 after a crappy placement but was g4 last season. would love to hear from you asap if i am needed
~ DemonzMercy

what role r u looking for?
i was gold 4 in eune, but i transferred here, and the transfer placement match as well as the new season placement matches messed my division up.
i could maybe join when i get internet tomorrow? (moved houses)
